        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a resident of Gujarat.\n1. The applicant must be a student. \n1. The applicant must belong to the Scheduled Tribe (ST) category.\n1. The applicant must have secured special merit in Matriculation, Higher Secondary, Indian School Certificate, or its equivalent examination.\n1. The applicant must have secured admission to a recognized foreign university for higher education.\n1. The applicant must have passed the Higher Secondary Certificate (HSC) or equivalent examination.\n\n<br>\n\n",
